WHY IT WORKS<\/div>\n  <h2 class=\"why-heading\">Your skin already knows what it needs. We just gave it that.<\/h2>\n  <p class=\"why-para\">Most moisturisers are 70% water with synthetic fillers — they sit on the surface, evaporate, and do nothing. Beef tallow is molecularly identical to your skin's natural oil. It absorbs completely, rebuilds your barrier, and works at the cellular level with vitamins A, D, E and K. <strong>Four ingredients. No fillers. Real glow.<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>","full_width":false,"show_divider":false,"padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"custom_liquid_cqKTNy":{"type":"custom-liquid","name":"t:sections.custom-liquid.presets.name","settings":{"custom_liquid":"<style>\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n  .rv-section {\n    background: #FFF8F3;\n    padding: 56px 0;\n    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n    text-align: center;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n  .rv-top { padding: 0 24px 40px; }\n  .rv-badge {\n    display: inline-block;\n    background: #D6608A;\n    color: #fff;\n    font-size: 12px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    letter-spacing: 0.1em;\n    padding: 8px 20px;\n    border-radius: 999px;\n    margin-bottom: 18px;\n  }\n  .rv-heading {\n    font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 38px);\n    font-weight: 800;\n    color: #4A3B42;\n  }\n  .rv-track-wrap {\n    width: 100%;\n    overflow-x: scroll;\n    overflow-y: visible;\n    scrollbar-width: none;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    cursor: grab;\n    padding: 4px 24px 16px;\n  }\n  .rv-track-wrap::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }\n  .rv-track {\n    display: inline-flex;\n    gap: 14px;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n  }\n  .rv-card {\n    display: inline-block;\n    vertical-align: top;\n    white-space: normal;\n    background: #fff;\n    border-radius: 16px;\n    width: 260px;\n    text-align: left;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(214, 96, 138, 0.08);\n  }\n  .ba-wrap {\n    width: 260px;\n    height: 200px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    background: #FDE3D6;\n  }\n  .ba-wrap img {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    object-fit: cover;\n    object-position: center top;\n    display: block;\n  }\n  .rv-body { padding: 16px; }\n  .rv-meta {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n  }\n  .rv-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #4A3B42; }\n  .rv-stars { color: #F5C842; font-size: 12px; }\n  .rv-tags {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    gap: 5px;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n  }\n  .rv-tag {\n    font-size: 9px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #D6608A;\n    background: #FDE3D6;\n    border: 1px solid #F8C8D4;\n    border-radius: 999px;\n    padding: 3px 8px;\n  }\n  .rv-quote {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #4A3B42;\n    margin-bottom: 6px;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  .rv-text {\n    font-size: 12px;\n    color: #9C7C86;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n  }\n  .rv-dots {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: center;\n    gap: 6px;\n    margin-top: 8px;\n    padding: 0 24px;\n  }\n  .rv-dot {\n    width: 8px;\n    height: 8px;\n    border-radius: 999px;\n    background: #F8C8D4;\n    border: none;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: all 0.25s;\n    padding: 0;\n  }\n  .rv-dot.active { background: #D6608A; width: 20px; }\n<\/style>\n\n<div class=\"rv-section\">\n  <div class=\"rv-top\">\n    <div class=\"rv-badge\">2,000+ JARS SOLD<\/div>\n    <h2 class=\"rv-heading\">Real Results. Real Glow.<\/h2>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div class=\"rv-track-wrap\" id=\"rvWrap\">\n    <div class=\"rv-track\" id=\"rvTrack\">\n\n      <div class=\"rv-card\">\n        <div class=\"ba-wrap\">\n          <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0957\/2981\/1738\/files\/Screenshot_2026-06-18_220300.png?v=1781809436\" alt=\"customer result\" \/>\n        <\/div>\n        <div class=\"rv-body\">\n          <div class=\"rv-meta\"><span class=\"rv-name\">Lara, 34<\/span><span class=\"rv-stars\">★★★★★<\/span><\/div>\n          <div class=\"rv-tags\"><span class=\"rv-tag\">WRINKLES SOFTENED<\/span><span class=\"rv-tag\">GLOW<\/span><\/div>\n          <p class=\"rv-quote\">\"My friends thought I got a facial.\"<\/p>\n          <p class=\"rv-text\">6 weeks in and everyone keeps asking what I changed. Just this jar, twice a day.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"rv-card\">\n        <div class=\"ba-wrap\">\n          <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0957\/2981\/1738\/files\/Screenshot_2026-06-18_220401.png?v=1781809455\" alt=\"customer result\" \/>\n        <\/div>\n        <div class=\"rv-body\">\n          <div class=\"rv-meta\"><span class=\"rv-name\">Nour, 41<\/span><span class=\"rv-stars\">★★★★★<\/span><\/div>\n          <div class=\"rv-tags\"><span class=\"rv-tag\">DRY SKIN FIXED<\/span><span class=\"rv-tag\">REDNESS GONE<\/span><\/div>\n          <p class=\"rv-quote\">\"Finally something that actually works.\"<\/p>\n          <p class=\"rv-text\">Tried everything at the pharmacy. This is the first thing that made my skin feel genuinely different.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"rv-card\">\n        <div class=\"rv-body\">\n          <div class=\"rv-meta\"><span class=\"rv-name\">Maya, 38<\/span><span class=\"rv-stars\">★★★★★<\/span><\/div>\n          <div class=\"rv-tags\"><span class=\"rv-tag\">SKIN BARRIER<\/span><span class=\"rv-tag\">NO MORE FLAKING<\/span><\/div>\n          <p class=\"rv-quote\">\"Sceptical at first. Not anymore.\"<\/p>\n          <p class=\"rv-text\">My cousin sent this from abroad. After a month the texture of my skin changed completely.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"rv-card\">\n        <div class=\"rv-body\">\n          <div class=\"rv-meta\"><span class=\"rv-name\">Rita, 45<\/span><span class=\"rv-stars\">★★★★★<\/span><\/div>\n          <div class=\"rv-tags\"><span class=\"rv-tag\">SUN DAMAGE<\/span><span class=\"rv-tag\">EVEN TONE<\/span><\/div>\n          <p class=\"rv-quote\">\"The Beirut sun does damage. This fixed it.\"<\/p>\n          <p class=\"rv-text\">Years of sun exposure left my skin rough. Four weeks in and my tone is more even than it's been in years.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"rv-card\">\n        <div class=\"rv-body\">\n          <div class=\"rv-meta\"><span class=\"rv-name\">Yara, 29<\/span><span class=\"rv-stars\">★★★★★<\/span><\/div>\n          <div class=\"rv-tags\"><span class=\"rv-tag\">ACNE REDUCED<\/span><span class=\"rv-tag\">LESS OILY<\/span><\/div>\n          <p class=\"rv-quote\">\"Cleared up what nothing else could.\"<\/p>\n          <p class=\"rv-text\">Had breakouts since I was a teenager. Two months in, clearest my skin has ever been.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"rv-card\">\n        <div class=\"rv-body\">\n          <div class=\"rv-meta\"><span class=\"rv-name\">Hala, 52<\/span><span class=\"rv-stars\">★★★★★<\/span><\/div>\n          <div class=\"rv-tags\"><span class=\"rv-tag\">ANTI-AGING<\/span><\/div>\n          <p class=\"rv-quote\">\"At my age I didn't expect results. I was wrong.\"<\/p>\n          <p class=\"rv-text\">My daughter ordered this as a joke. Three weeks later she's using it too. Skin hasn't looked this good since my 30s.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"rv-card\">\n        <div class=\"rv-body\">\n          <div class=\"rv-meta\"><span class=\"rv-name\">Tala, 36<\/span><span class=\"rv-stars\">★★★★★<\/span><\/div>\n          <div class=\"rv-tags\"><span class=\"rv-tag\">NATURAL GLOW<\/span><\/div>\n          <p class=\"rv-quote\">\"This is my little secret now.\"<\/p>\n          <p class=\"rv-text\">I was sceptical about a tallow balm. Now I tell every girl I know. The results do all the talking.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"rv-card\">\n        <div class=\"rv-body\">\n          <div class=\"rv-meta\"><span class=\"rv-name\">Jana, 31<\/span><span class=\"rv-stars\">★★★★★<\/span><\/div>\n          <div class=\"rv-tags\"><span class=\"rv-tag\">REDNESS GONE<\/span><\/div>\n          <p class=\"rv-quote\">\"Irritation gone in two weeks.\"<\/p>\n          <p class=\"rv-text\">My skin was always red and reactive. This calmed it down completely. Nothing else came close.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"rv-card\">\n        <div class=\"rv-body\">\n          <div class=\"rv-meta\"><span class=\"rv-name\">Carla, 44<\/span><span class=\"rv-stars\">★★★★★<\/span><\/div>\n          <div class=\"rv-tags\"><span class=\"rv-tag\">WRINKLES SOFTENED<\/span><\/div>\n          <p class=\"rv-quote\">\"Worth every lira.\"<\/p>\n          <p class=\"rv-text\">Spent a lot on skincare over the years. First time I felt the money was actually justified. Skin looks younger, feels stronger.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"rv-card\">\n        <div class=\"rv-body\">\n          <div class=\"rv-meta\"><span class=\"rv-name\">Dana, 33<\/span><span class=\"rv-stars\">★★★★★<\/span><\/div>\n          <div class=\"rv-tags\"><span class=\"rv-tag\">WINTER SKIN<\/span><span class=\"rv-tag\">HYDRATION<\/span><\/div>\n          <p class=\"rv-quote\">\"Survived the Beirut winter for the first time.\"<\/p>\n          <p class=\"rv-text\">Every winter my skin cracks and peels badly. Used this from October — face stayed smooth the whole season.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"rv-card\">\n        <div class=\"rv-body\">\n          <div class=\"rv-meta\"><span class=\"rv-name\">Lynn, 39<\/span><span class=\"rv-stars\">★★★★★<\/span><\/div>\n          <div class=\"rv-tags\"><span class=\"rv-tag\">DARK CIRCLES<\/span><span class=\"rv-tag\">TIRED LOOK<\/span><\/div>\n          <p class=\"rv-quote\">\"I look less tired even when I am tired.\"<\/p>\n          <p class=\"rv-text\">The area under my eyes was always dark and puffy. After three weeks I genuinely look more awake.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"rv-card\">\n        <div class=\"rv-body\">\n          <div class=\"rv-meta\"><span class=\"rv-name\">Rana, 47<\/span><span class=\"rv-stars\">★★★★★<\/span><\/div>\n          <div class=\"rv-tags\"><span class=\"rv-tag\">SENSITIVE SKIN<\/span><\/div>\n          <p class=\"rv-quote\">\"My skin reacts to everything. Not this.\"<\/p>\n          <p class=\"rv-text\">I've tried dozens of creams and always broke out. This is the first product that didn't irritate me at all. And it actually worked.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div class=\"rv-dots\" id=\"rvDots\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<script>\n  const wrap = document.getElementById('rvWrap');\n  const track = document.getElementById('rvTrack');\n  const dotsEl = document.getElementById('rvDots');\n  const cards = track.querySelectorAll('.rv-card');\n  const count = cards.length;\n\n  for (let i = 0; i < count; i++) {\n    const d = document.createElement('button');\n    d.className = 'rv-dot' + (i === 0 ? ' active' : '');\n    d.addEventListener('click', () => {\n      wrap.scrollTo({ left: cards[i].offsetLeft - 24, behavior: 'smooth' });\n    });\n    dotsEl.appendChild(d);\n  }\n  const allDots = dotsEl.querySelectorAll('.rv-dot');\n\n  wrap.addEventListener('scroll', () => {\n    let closest = 0, minDist = Infinity;\n    cards.forEach((c, i) => {\n      const dist = Math.abs(c.offsetLeft - wrap.scrollLeft - 24);\n      if (dist < minDist) { minDist = dist; closest = i; }\n    });\n    allDots.forEach((d, i) => d.classList.toggle('active', i === closest));\n  });\n\n  let drag = false, startX = 0, startScroll = 0;\n  wrap.addEventListener('mousedown', e => {\n    drag = true; startX = e.pageX; startScroll = wrap.scrollLeft;\n    wrap.style.cursor = 'grabbing'; e.preventDefault();\n  });\n  window.addEventListener('mouseup', () => { drag = false; wrap.style.cursor = 'grab'; });\n  window.addEventListener('mousemove', e => {\n    if (!drag) return;\n    wrap.scrollLeft = startScroll - (e.pageX - startX);\n  });\n<\/script>","full_width":false,"show_divider":false,"padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"scrolling_promotion_6Xj9FQ":{"type":"scrolling-promotion","blocks":{"announcement_QJYrYr":{"type":"announcement","settings":{"icon":"none","icon_size":"medium","custom_icon":"","text":"FREE DELIVERY ALL OVER LEBANON","text_size":20,"link":""}}},"block_order":["announcement_QJYrYr"],"name":"t:sections.scrolling-promotion.presets.name","settings":{"direction":"left","speed":1.6,"show_divider":false,"use_custom_colors":true,"colors_icon":"#ffffff","colors_text":"#000000","colors_background":"#e7d5c7","gradient_background":"","padding_top":20,"padding_bottom":20}},"image_with_text_X6KRyA":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_Y6bCpT":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Natural-Looking Freckles (No Skill, No Effort)","heading_size":"h1","heading_tag":"h2"}},"text_fXwrbU":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Tired of <strong>uneven <\/strong>dots, streaky pencils, or freckles that look fake by lunchtime? This multi-point freckle stamp was built for real <strong>humans <\/strong>— not makeup artists.<\/p>","text_size":"typeset2","secondary_color":false}}},"block_order":["heading_Y6bCpT","text_fXwrbU"],"disabled":true,"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/73869677-F4A8-4401-8032-7FD4C16C25BD_1060x_0331b5a5-d549-4c42-aed4-bc24160e24f9.png","image_position":"center center","layout":"image_first","text_box_position":"middle","text_alignment":"left","image_ratio":"650px","enlarge_content":false,"full_width":false,"show_divider":false,"image_behavior":"none","mobile_layout":"image_first","mobile_text_alignment":"left","mobile_image_ratio":"auto","enable_video_looping":false,"video_url":"","use_custom_colors":false,"colors_button_label":"#ffffff","colors_button_background":"#1a1b18","colors_text":"#212326","colors_background":"#ffffff","gradient_background":"","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"scrolling_promotion_pD6Mdt":{"type":"scrolling-promotion","blocks":{"announcement_CR4hbT":{"type":"announcement","settings":{"icon":"none","icon_size":"medium","custom_icon":"","text":"FREE DELIVERY ALL OVER LEBANON","text_size":20,"link":""}}},"block_order":["announcement_CR4hbT"],"disabled":true,"name":"t:sections.scrolling-promotion.presets.name","settings":{"direction":"left","speed":1.6,"show_divider":false,"use_custom_colors":true,"colors_icon":"#ffffff","colors_text":"#000000","colors_background":"#e7d5c7","gradient_background":"","padding_top":20,"padding_bottom":20}},"custom_liquid_QWbLRi":{"type":"custom-liquid","name":"t:sections.custom-liquid.presets.name","settings":{"custom_liquid":"<style>\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n  .li-section {\n    background: #FFF8F3;\n    padding: 64px 24px;\n    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    gap: 48px;\n    justify-content: center;\n    align-items: center;\n    max-width: 1200px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n  .li-left { flex: 1 1 380px; max-width: 500px; }\n  .li-left img { width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 20px; display: block; }\n  .li-right { flex: 1 1 420px; max-width: 560px; }\n  .li-heading {\n    font-size: clamp(30px, 4.5vw, 46px);\n    font-weight: 900;\n    line-height: 1.1;\n    color: #4A3B42;\n    margin: 0 0 22px;\n  }\n  .li-heading span { color: #D6608A; display: block; }\n  .li-intro { font-size: 16px; color: #9C7C86; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 18px; }\n  .li-warn { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #4A3B42; margin: 0 0 26px; }\n  .li-card { border: 1px solid #F8C8D4; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; background: #fff; }\n  .li-card-head {\n    background: #FDE3D6; text-align: center; font-size: 15px;\n    font-weight: 700; color: #D6608A; padding: 14px;\n  }\n  .li-stat {\n    display: flex; gap: 18px; align-items: center;\n    padding: 22px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #FBE9E0;\n  }\n  .li-stat:last-child { border-bottom: none; }\n  .li-circle {\n    flex-shrink: 0; width: 76px; height: 76px; border-radius: 50%;\n    background: #F8C8D4; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\n    font-size: 22px; font-weight: 900; color: #D6608A;\n    animation: pop 0.6s ease-out both;\n  }\n  @keyframes pop {\n    0% { transform: scale(0.4); opacity: 0; }\n    70% { transform: scale(1.1); }\n    100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }\n  }\n  .li-stat:nth-child(3) .li-circle { animation-delay: 0.15s; }\n  .li-stat:nth-child(4) .li-circle { animation-delay: 0.3s; }\n  .li-stat-title { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; color: #4A3B42; margin: 0 0 6px; }\n  .li-stat-text { font-size: 14px; color: #9C7C86; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }\n<\/style>\n\n<div class=\"li-section\">\n  <div class=\"li-left\">\n    \n  <\/div>\n\n  <div class=\"li-right\">\n    <h2 class=\"li-heading\">The Skincare Industry Is <span>Lying To Your Face<\/span><\/h2>\n    <p class=\"li-intro\">Most lotions and creams are filled with seed oils, parabens, toxic fragrances, and phthalates — chemicals that don't just rest on your skin. They penetrate your bloodstream, mess with your hormones, and disrupt your body's natural rhythm.<\/p>\n    <p class=\"li-warn\">These aren't just ineffective — they're actively harmful.<\/p>\n\n    <div class=\"li-card\">\n      <div class=\"li-card-head\">Shocking Industry Statistic<\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"li-stat\">\n        <div class=\"li-circle\">78%<\/div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"li-stat-title\">Hormone-Disrupting Fragrances<\/h3>\n          <p class=\"li-stat-text\">78% of lotions use synthetic fragrances that trigger inflammation, breakouts, and hormone imbalance.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"li-stat\">\n        <div class=\"li-circle\">85%<\/div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"li-stat-title\">Hormone-Suppressing Chemicals<\/h3>\n          <p class=\"li-stat-text\">85% of body lotions contain lab-made ingredients linked to hormone suppression and health risks.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"li-stat\">\n        <div class=\"li-circle\">87%<\/div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"li-stat-title\">Pore-Clogging Petroleum<\/h3>\n          <p class=\"li-stat-text\">87% of drugstore moisturizers use petroleum that coats your skin and blocks it from breathing.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>","full_width":false,"show_divider":false,"padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"custom_liquid_PyWqQE":{"type":"custom-liquid","name":"t:sections.custom-liquid.presets.name","settings":{"custom_liquid":"<style>\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n  .faq-section {\n    background: #FFF8F3;\n    padding: 64px 24px;\n    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n  .faq-heading {\n    font-size: clamp(22px, 5vw, 40px);\n    font-weight: 900;\n    color: #4A3B42;\n    letter-spacing: -0.01em;\n    margin-bottom: 14px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n  }\n  .faq-sub {\n    font-size: 15px;\n    color: #9C7C86;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    max-width: 560px;\n    margin: 0 auto 48px;\n  }\n  .faq-list {\n    max-width: 720px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    text-align: left;\n  }\n  .faq-item {\n    border-top: 1px solid #F3D9D0;\n    background: transparent;\n  }\n  .faq-item:last-child {\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #F3D9D0;\n  }\n  .faq-question {\n    width: 100%;\n    background: transparent;\n    border: none;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n    padding: 20px 4px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    gap: 16px;\n    text-align: left;\n  }\n  .faq-question span {\n    font-size: 15px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #4A3B42;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n    flex: 1;\n  }\n  .faq-icon {\n    font-size: 22px;\n    font-weight: 300;\n    color: #D6608A;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    line-height: 1;\n    transition: transform 0.25s;\n    width: 24px;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n  .faq-item.open .faq-icon {\n    transform: rotate(45deg);\n  }\n  .faq-item.open .faq-question {\n    background: #FDE3D6;\n    padding-left: 12px;\n    padding-right: 12px;\n    border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;\n  }\n  .faq-item.open .faq-question span { color: #D6608A; }\n  .faq-answer {\n    display: none;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #7A6068;\n    line-height: 1.75;\n    padding: 16px 12px 22px;\n    background: #FDE3D6;\n    border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;\n  }\n  .faq-item.open .faq-answer {\n    display: block;\n  }\n<\/style>\n\n<div class=\"faq-section\">\n  <h2 class=\"faq-heading\">Frequently Asked Questions<\/h2>\n  <p class=\"faq-sub\">We understand that investing in your skin is a big decision. That's why we're here to help you make an informed choice.<\/p>\n\n  <div class=\"faq-list\" id=\"faqList\">\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item open\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">\n        <span>What ingredients are in the Tallow Balm?<\/span>\n        <div class=\"faq-icon\">+<\/div>\n      <\/button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        Only 4 natural ingredients: grass-fed, grass-finished beef tallow, cold-pressed organic olive oil, organic manuka honey, and organic beeswax. No fillers, no chemicals — just raw, unadulterated skin nutrition that helps your skin thrive naturally.\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">\n        <span>Do your products contain any artificial fragrances?<\/span>\n        <div class=\"faq-icon\">+<\/div>\n      <\/button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        No — completely free from artificial fragrances. Any scent comes naturally from the ingredients themselves. This makes it ideal for those with sensitivities to synthetic fragrances or anyone seeking truly natural skincare.\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">\n        <span>Is this suitable for sensitive skin?<\/span>\n        <div class=\"faq-icon\">+<\/div>\n      <\/button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        Yes. The natural fat profile in grass-fed tallow closely resembles human skin cells, making it highly compatible and gentle. Many customers with eczema, rosacea, and other skin sensitivities report significant improvements after switching to this balm.\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">\n        <span>Does the balm have a smell?<\/span>\n        <div class=\"faq-icon\">+<\/div>\n      <\/button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        The Unscented version has a very light, natural scent from the pure ingredients — no added fragrance. Most people describe it as neutral and barely noticeable once applied. If you choose Citrus or Lavender, the scent comes only from natural essential oils — gentle, clean, and never overpowering.\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">\n        <span>How do I apply the Tallow Balm?<\/span>\n        <div class=\"faq-icon\">+<\/div>\n      <\/button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        Take a small amount — about the size of a pea for the face — and warm it between your fingertips. It melts slightly with body heat, making it easy to spread. Gently massage into clean skin using upward, circular motions until fully absorbed. A little goes a long way.\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">\n        <span>How often should I use it?<\/span>\n        <div class=\"faq-icon\">+<\/div>\n      <\/button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        For best results, use 1–2 times daily on clean skin. Most women use it morning and night. Those with very dry skin may benefit from more frequent application, while those with oilier skin might prefer once daily — typically in the evening.\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">\n        <span>Can I use the Tallow Balm on my face?<\/span>\n        <div class=\"faq-icon\">+<\/div>\n      <\/button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        Absolutely. Its natural composition mirrors human skin cells, making it ideal for facial use. It's deeply moisturising without clogging pores and helps balance oil production, reduce fine lines, and soothe irritation.\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">\n        <span>Will this cause breakouts?<\/span>\n        <div class=\"faq-icon\">+<\/div>\n      <\/button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        No. Grass-fed beef tallow is bioidentical to human sebum — your pores recognise it and absorb it completely. Unlike synthetic oils that sit on the surface, tallow penetrates naturally and is non-comedogenic. Many customers with acne-prone or oily skin actually report clearer skin after switching from conventional moisturisers.\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">\n        <span>What is your return policy?<\/span>\n        <div class=\"faq-icon\">+<\/div>\n      <\/button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        We offer a 90-Day Results Guarantee — not a standard return window. If you don't see visible improvement within 90 days of consistent use, contact us and we'll refund every cent. No questions asked. No return required. You don't even need to send the jar back.\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">\n        <span>When will I receive my order?<\/span>\n        <div class=\"faq-icon\">+<\/div>\n      <\/button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        All orders are processed and shipped within 1–2 business days. Once shipped, you'll receive a tracking link automatically. Estimated delivery is 3–5 business days. No hidden fees or surprise charges at checkout.\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<script>\n  document.getElementById('faqList').addEventListener('click', function(e) {\n    const btn = e.target.closest('.faq-question');\n    if (!btn) return;\n    const item = btn.closest('.faq-item');\n    const isOpen = item.classList.contains('open');\n    document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(i => i.classList.remove('open'));\n    if (!isOpen) item.classList.add('open');\n  });\n<\/script>","full_width":true,"show_divider":false,"padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}}},"order":["empty-space","main","product-recommendations","custom_liquid_KL9pzK","custom_liquid_cqKTNy","scrolling_promotion_6Xj9FQ","image_with_text_X6KRyA","scrolling_promotion_pD6Mdt","custom_liquid_QWbLRi","custom_liquid_PyWqQE"]}